@echo off
cls * *** Clears the screen (In DOS mode) *** *
echo * ******************************************************************************* * echo * *** runs all netstat commands *** * echo * *** netstat -a - Dipslays all connections and listerning ports *** * echo * *** netstat -n - Displays addresses and port numbers in numerical form *** * echo * *** netstat -r - Displays the routing table *** * echo * *** netstat -s - Displays per-protocol statistics *** * echo * *** netstat -e - Displays Ethernet statistics *** * echo * ******************************************************************************* *
if "%1" == "" goto NOWAIT if NOT "%1" == " " goto WITHWAIT
:NOWAIT REM netstat -a REM _sleep 1
netstat -n _sleep 1
netstat -r _sleep 1
netstat -s _sleep 1
netstat -e _sleep 1 goto END
:WITHWAIT rem netstat -a rem _sleep %1
netstat -n rem _sleep %1
netstat -r rem _sleep %1
netstat -s rem _sleep %1
netstat -e _sleep %1 goto END
:END echo * ******************************************************************************* * echo * *** setting exit code 00 *** * echo * ******************************************************************************* * _exit 00
